<paragraph blockId="3.[151,619,1122,1149]" box="[151,619,1122,1149]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,619,1122,1149]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,619,1122,1149]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">
Genus 
<taxonomicName authority="von Siebold 1856" authorityName="von Siebold" authorityYear="1856" box="[238,619,1122,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Helicopsychidae" genus="Helicopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[238,399,1122,1149]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Helicopsyche</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="von Siebold, C. T. E." box="[407,619,1122,1149]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" refId="ref6804" refString="von Siebold, C. T. E. (1856) Wahre Parthenogenesis bei Schmetterlingen und Bienen. Ein Beitrag zur Fortpflanzungsgeschichte der Thiere. Engelmann, Leipzig, 133 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 10708" type="book" year="1856">von Siebold 1856</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="581" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1195,1293]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">
This genus has been divided into two subgenera (
<emphasis box="[729,869,1195,1221]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Ferropsyche</emphasis>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Müller" authorityYear="1885" box="[930,1095,1195,1221]" class="Insecta" family="Helicopsychidae" genus="Cochliopsyche" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[930,1095,1195,1221]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Cochliopsyche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) in the Neotropics (
<bibRefCitation author="Johanson, K. A." pageId="3" pageNumber="581" pagination="1 - 172" refId="ref5932" refString="Johanson, K. A. (1998) Phylogenetic and biogeographic analysis of the family Helicopsychidae (Insecta: Trichoptera). Entomologica Scandinavica, Supplement, 53, 1 - 172." type="journal article" year="1998">Johanson 1998</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Holzenthal, R. W. &amp; Calor, A. R." box="[222,512,1231,1257]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" pagination="1 - 566" refId="ref5887" refString="Holzenthal, R. W. &amp; Calor, A. R. (2017) Catalog of the Neotropical Trichoptera (Caddisflies). Zookeys, 654, 1 - 566. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 654.9516" type="journal article" year="2017">Holzenthal &amp; Calor 2017</bibRefCitation>
). The current 14 species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="von Siebold" authorityYear="1856" box="[823,974,1231,1257]" class="Insecta" family="Helicopsychidae" genus="Helicopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[823,974,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Helicopsyche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[1010,1099,1231,1257]" name="Panama" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Panama</collectingCountry>
all belong to the 
<emphasis box="[1296,1436,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Ferropsyche</emphasis>
subgenus (
<bibRefCitation author="Armitage, B. J. &amp; Harris, S. C. &amp; Arefina-Armitage, T. I. &amp; Cornejo, A." box="[270,506,1266,1293]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" pagination="1 - 16" refId="ref4687" refString="Armitage, B. J., Harris, S. C., Arefina-Armitage, T. I. &amp; Cornejo, A. (2015) The Trichoptera of Panama. III. Updated species list for caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) in the Republic of Panama. Insecta Mundi, 0442, 1 - 16." type="book chapter" year="2015">
Armitage 
<emphasis box="[384,434,1267,1293]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">et al</emphasis>
. 2015
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Armitage, B. J. &amp; Harris, S. C. &amp; Blahnik, R. J. &amp; Thomson, R. E. &amp; Rios Gonzalez, T. A. &amp; Aguirre, Y." box="[517,578,1267,1293]" pageId="3" pageNumber="581" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref4747" refString="Armitage, B. J., Harris, S. C., Blahnik, R. J., Thomson, R. E., Rios Gonzalez, T. A. &amp; Aguirre, Y. (2020) The Trichoptera of Panama XIII. Further new country records for caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from the Republic of Panama. Insecta Mundi, 0744, 1 - 8." type="book chapter" year="2020">2020</bibRefCitation>
). Herein we add one more species from central 
<collectingCountry box="[1111,1203,1267,1293]" name="Panama" pageId="3" pageNumber="581">Panama</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
